Description:
UNDER OFFER - Incredible Harbour, CBD And Stadium Views!
With a floorplan that maximizes space and a balcony that promises incredible views of Victoria Harbour, the city, and Etihad Stadium, this classy two bedroom corner apartment shines in the popular NewQuay precinct.
The coveted ‘Harbour 1’ complex is the setting for this 20th floor property, which excels thanks to bright full windows, stone surfaces, and a stunning open layout. Spend day and night in the relaxed lounge and dining zone, while summers nights will have you utilising the large covered balcony with views to the south and west.
Both bedrooms have the same great space and built-in robes, meanwhile the quality bathroom comes with a European laundry and the gleaming kitchen is functional for easy breakfasts, lunches, and dinners. Other extras include central heating and cooling, intercom entry, storage cage, secure car space, and access to a library lounge, media room, and gym.
Moments to The District Docklands, restaurants including Medici Docklands, Fish Bar, and Achelya Restaurant, IGA X-press supermarket, Etihad Stadium, and trams to Bundoora RMIT and the CBD.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
Pristine, Light-Filled and Offering Remarkable Views
Lasting modern appeal combines with relaxed light-filled living, city and river views and a sensational Yarra’s Edge location to deliver one of the Dockland’s best two bedroom + study, two bathroom apartments.
This exquisite parkside pad is pristinely presented for keen owner-occupiers who can come in and live straight away. Tall windows brings in the brilliant natural light especially through the expansive lounge and dining zone, which also includes the state of the art kitchen owning a stone island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances.
The large undercover balcony is the optimal space to marvel at the inspired Yarra River and city skyline views. A handy study/bedroom area offers further flexibility, meanwhile the amazing master bedroom has its own designer ensuite, large built-in robes and a private balcony. Further enjoy a gorgeous main bathroom, laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry and two secure car spaces.
Being in the stunning Yarra’s Edge precinct also allows you access to RekDek facilities which include a gym, pool, spa, steam room and sauna. You’re also just a stone’s throw to amazing South Wharf Promenade restaurants, Polly Woodside, DFO shopping, Port Melbourne attractions, Crown Casino, trams and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
YARRAS EDGE GEM
Poised perfectly on the front of Tower 2 overlooking the Marina, this naturally lit North facing apartment offers sensational value. A spacious gourmet kitchen with ample work space including a removable island bench with plenty of space to entertain friends and family. The lounge leads onto a spacious large terrace overlooking the harbour and capturing the northern sunshine. The Master bedroom offers walk-in robes, ensuite and private second balcony with views over the Docks. Perfect temperature all round with ducted heating and cooling. Within walking distance of South Wharf, waterfront restaurants, Southern Cross and the City, this is ultimate waterfront living. This apartment is priced to sell and ready to be sold! An allocated car space is also included in the title.
- Stunning North facing Yarra & marina views from level 6
- Highly desired two bedroom floorplan with floor-to-ceiling windows
- Master bedroom with walk-in-robe, ensuite and second balcony with marina views
- Large gourmet kitchen, plenty of storage, removable island bench & stainless appliances
- Spacious living room with direct access to private and protected terrace
- Secure car space and ducted air-con / heating throughout
- Tower 2 location on Yarra's Edge, CBD access, Southbank & Port Melbourne
- Access to residents pool, gym, spa, sauna and steam room
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:
Renovated Arkley Oasis with stunning Harbour Vistas
Boasting a brilliant position on the 14th floor of the exclusive Arkley residential complex, this fully renovated two bedroom, two bathroom apartment combines luxury modern class with tremendous views of Victoria Harbour.
This is a wonderful chance for owner-occupiers to embrace a stylish waterside lifestyle, with this well-presented property showcasing sensational harbour views from both the sizeable undercover balcony and the central living and meals zone which is filled with stunning natural light.
The sublime kitchen has beautiful marble benchtops, a convenient breakfast bar, quality stainless steel appliances, and Fisher & Paykel fridge and freezer. The master bedroom comes with a study nook, built-in robe, and an ensuite, while the second bedroom also delivers great BIR storage. Further enjoy a pristine bathroom, European laundry with Miele washer dryer, timber floors, reverse cycle cooling and heating, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a pool, spa, golf practice net, and gym.
This complex is named after notable Australian artist Howard Arkley. You have access to local restaurants including Steakhouse Grill 66, Docklands Pizzeria, Mint-o-Mustard, and Bhoj Restaurant, while you’re also close to the new District Docklands, Etihad Stadium, and trams taking you to West Preston, Bundoora RMIT, and the city.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556

Description:
Massive 60sqm Single Bedroom in Stunning Quays Class
Boasting an expansive living zone, tremendous views of the iconic CBD and a place in the amazing Quays complex which has outstanding building facilities, this supersized one bedroom apartment is true Docklands brilliance.
This 6th floor retreat is the perfect match for owner-occupiers and city professionals who desire great space and modern class. The generous central lounge and dining zone is an extra-large size you ordinarily won’t find in a one bedroom apartment, with the gourmet kitchen perfect for preparing meals thanks to a practical design and quality stainless steel Miele appliances.
The undercover balcony offers superb views of the city, while the sizeable bedroom also with CBD vistas has a built-in robe and is just steps to the pristine bathroom. Also enjoy a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and a secure car space.
Access a Health Club featuring a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, as well as the Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. There is also a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
Embrace the NewQuay precinct close to The District Docklands, Costco, Etihad Stadium, restaurants including The Conder restaurant, New Quay International Buffet, Achelya Restaurant, and Waterside Oriental Bistro, and trams.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
BEAUTIFUL PENTHOUSE APARTMENT
A once in a lifetime opportunity beckons in the heart of the Docklands with this remarkable 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 3 car spaces dual level apartment. Enormous both inside and out and oozing opulence with an expansive living zone, 3 spacious upstairs bedrooms, and a 152 sqm terrace with stunning views, this flawless gem is near Etihad Stadium and a plethora of Docklands attractions.
Accommodation: Towering floor-to-ceiling windows, plush surfaces, and a sense of gracious style underline this unique residence, which sits on 216 sqm internally, highlighted by the expansive living area with adjoining kitchen boasting Miele appliances and an island benchtop. Through the sliding doors is the massive terrace, which enjoys 40th floor views of the CBD, Port Phillip Bay, and Docklands waterfront. All 3 upstairs bedrooms are stylish and spacious, none more so than the master bed which has access to a 2nd private balcony and lush ensuite, while the luxury main bath is fitted with a spa.
Features: 3 secure car spaces, 2 side-by-side and all 3 on the 3rd floor, two huge storage cages, downstairs powder room, ducted heating and cooling, separate laundry, video intercom and a resident Building Manager.
For an inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:

Located in the Victoria Harbour precinct of Docklands, this appealing 1 bedroom apartment is perfect for either an owner occupier or astute investor.
This superb apartment features:
- Open plan living and dining area adjoins balcony
- Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances incorporating Fisher & Paykel Drawer dishwasher, Blanco Oven and induction stove
- Bedroom with built-in mirrored robes,
- Split system air conditioning,
- Fully tiled bathroom with European laundry,
- Double glazed windows,
- Security entrance
- Lift access.
Facilities include: a residents lounge and communal garden.
Within close proximity to the Woolworths, situated in the free tram zone, Australia Post Office and only moments from Southern Cross Station, this apartment would appeal to those looking for a central location in the heart of the Docklands.
Buy your slice of the Docklands
Deposit: 10%
Settlement: 30 days

Description:
The Best Array of Views
Soaring above the Conder, captivating views as far as the eye can see will amaze.
From the lights of the City skyline, across the harbour, over Port Phillip Bay and towards magnificent sunsets behind the Bolte Bridge are simply dazzling.
Located in the Quays residential complex, this fantastic 3 bedroom apartment on the 29th floor, awaits the discerning buyer looking for that wow factor.
Modern kitchen with an island bench presents ample storage. Integrated stainless steel Miele appliances consisting of an oven with a gas stove top, provides the perfect set up for a budding chef.
Spacious open plan dining and living area with full length floor to ceiling windows adjoins an east facing covered balcony, ideal for outdoor entertaining and setting up for a BBQ .
Main bedroom consists of a study nook and Stylish ensuite. The 2nd bedroom with mirrored robes also with an ensuite, whilst the 3rd bedroom shares a central bathroom.
Great features include
• 2 side by side car spaces
• Split system reverse cycle heating and cooling.
• Floorboards in living, dining and bedroom areas
• East and West Security entrances
• Double glazed windows
• NBN Internet ready
The complex sports full facilities which include an indoor pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, cinema, communal BBQ area with landscaped gardens, theatre and a tennis court.
Close proximity to the CBD, situated in the free tram zone and close to Southern Cross station. Easy access to the freeway and smooth travels to Melbourne airport.

Description:
Nest or invest
Located on the 15th floor of the Arkley complex (named after notable Australian artist Howard Arkley), this immaculate property has living highlights galore. The astounding harbour views is an aspect of this apartment you’ll never get tired of, with the main undercover balcony the best vantage point to enjoy these picturesque vistas.
A central living and dining zone has fantastic space and is adjoined by a gorgeous gourmet kitchen fitted with a handy stone breakfast bar and premium stainless steel appliances. The main bedroom has the benefit of its own north-facing balcony which has views of the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, while both bedrooms comes with built-in robe storage.
You’ll also get a well-appointed bathroom with a separate powder room, European laundry, reverse cycle cooling and heating, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a pool, spa, golf practice net, and gym. Moments to excellent harbourside restaurants including Steakhouse Grill 66, Bhoj Restaurant, and Docklands Pizzeria. Also near new District Docklands, Etihad Stadium, and trams taking you to West Preston, Bundoora RMIT, and the city.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing
Photos are for illustration purpose only

A Marvellous Addition to Your Docklands Investment Portfolio
Perfect for the savvy investor interested in a smart and sleek addition to the portfolio, or a CBD professional who wants a stylish modern pad that is an easy commute to work, this one bedroom apartment sets the gold standard.
In the ‘Gold Tower’ of the coveted Aqui development, this north-facing retreat has exceptional highlights including a light-filled main lounge and dining zone, undercover balcony with terrific northerly views including the Melbourne Star Observational Wheel best enjoyed at night, stone-featured kitchen with black tapware and Miele appliances, bedroom with mirrored BIR, elegant bathroom with rain shower and European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, and secure intercom.
Access a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, rooftop garden, and secure on-site bicycle storage. Positioned right opposite the new The District Docklands and seconds the brilliant waterside restaurants, IGA X-Press, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 35, 70, and 86 trams taking you everywhere!

Embracing waterfront living with contemporary architectural innovation, 883 Collins Street represents Melbourne's affluent evolution. Description:
A Yarra’s Edge Beauty That Ticks all the Boxes
From the clever floorplan and luxurious interiors to remarkable views of the Yarra River and parts of Southbank and the CBD, this elegant two bedroom + study, two bathroom apartment is your chance to live the modern Docklands good life.
Bright floor-to-ceiling windows, quality stone benchtops, excellent tapware, and other premium touches is what sets this residence apart from the rest. The large undercover balcony can be accessed via the spacious living and meals zones, with this special alfresco space taking in the beautiful water views with Southbank and city buildings completing the picturesque backdrop.
The opulent kitchen is also practical with an island bench and stainless steel appliances. A dedicated study has its own privacy as do both bedrooms which includes the excellent master bedroom which offers a dual vanity ensuite and another balcony. Also make the most of a gorgeous central bathroom, concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
You have super easy access to the city, Port Melbourne, Southbank, and South Melbourne, while walk to South Wharf and enjoy terrific spots including Meat Market, Common Man, West Village NYC. Also near DFO shops, Crown Casino, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Heritage Charm
No car required. The tram stop is at your door step, Southern Cross train station is across the road and Crown Casino is only across the bridge. Fully furnished Studio style apartment in Melbourne's Grandest of buildings, brimming with charm and character, the unit is fully refurbished and offers spacious lounge/Bedroom and kitchen/dinning leading to a large East facing balcony providing ample natural light. The building was originally opened in 1893 and refurbished in 1996 to accommodate a mix of serviced and residential apartments. Features include ducted heating and cooling, pool, spa, sauna, and gymnasium, caretaker, piano Bar, restaurant and cafe. This is ideal for professionals seeking the great City life or investors wanting a good solid investment with good secure returns. Hurry this will not last long. For a private inspection call Richard 0437 250 964

Description:
A Stunning Outlook
This spectacular & unique apartment boasts a never-to-be-built-out 270 degree view, which will continue to evolve & mature over the next decade as Melbourne continues to embrace Dockland's 7km's of waterfront as the city doubles its footprint from 200 to 400 hectares. Soak up the supreme style, comfort & magnificent views that the luxurious high-rise home offers. Designed with optimum functionality in mind, the contemporary layout showcases generous living/dining wrapped with sheets of glass framing the mesmerising panoramas to ensure an intimate relationship with the stunning scenic surrounds including the Yarra, Docklands Park, Port Phillip bay, Victoria Harbour, City Circle trams & night-time display of the Southern Cross Star's lights. The Smeg-appointed kitchen is perfectly positioned to take in the spectacular views while cooking. An entertaining terrace can be accessed from the master ensuite bedroom, which incorporates a study nook. The apartment also features a second bedroom & bathroom, laundry taps, ducted heating & cooling, video monitored entry & car space. Residents also enjoy the facilities of a heated outdoor salt pool & spa, gym, sauna, outdoor area & a free business centre for private events. Nestled between Bourke & Collins street in the South tower of the prestigious Watergate complex, this is a brilliant inner-city opportunity within walking distance to the best that this dynamic Docklands precinct has to offer including parks, community gardens, Free Tram zone, Etihad Stadium, Harbour Town, DFO, Southern Cross Station, Supermarkets & popular bars, cafe's & restaurants.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:
3 Balconies, 2 Car Spaces, 1 Outstanding Living Experience
A complete triumph when it comes to utterly luxurious and stunningly spacious apartment living in the prestigious Yarra’s Edge residential complex, this amazing 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence has a 17th floor position as well as three separate balconies!
This impeccable property needs to be seen to be believed, with a considered floorplan allowing for both open and private living. You’ll spend hours lazing about in the relaxed central lounge and dining spaces, with this vast area adjoined by a stone kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. This space also opens out to a balcony which takes in breathtaking views of the CBD and marina below.
The master bedroom is privately tucked away from the main living hub and comes with a dual vanity ensuite, BIRs, and a balcony, while a 2nd bedroom also has a balcony. The 3rd bedroom is situated right near the deluxe central and handy powder room which also has a European laundry.
On top of these main features, this apartment also comes with ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. Don’t miss this amazing opportunity!
The Yarra’s Edge is a premium destination for those looking to make the Docklands switch. You’re located close to the amazing South Wharf which has a variety if sensational bars and restaurants as well as easy access to DFO shopping. This area is also near Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and just over the Webb Bridge to the terrific Victoria Harbour precinct.

Description:
The Perfect Paradise
This impressive and spacious 2 bedroom apartment with views to the city skyline is ideal for buyers looking for an abode with a private courtyard, perfect for families, pet owners or those that enjoy outdoor entertaining.
Named after leading Australian painter Arthur Boyd, the Boyd tower exemplifies how the Docklands landscape has developed from humble beginnings.
Located on level 4 of the complex, the residence offers a superb layout. A stylish kitchen with integrated stainless steel appliances and large bench top provides ease of use for the chef, and central entertaining area for guests. Open plan dining and living area leads onto the massive outdoor space, and continuing through a private gate will take you to the manicured common garden area. Spacious main bedroom with ensuite, study alcove and built in robes, and second bedroom also with built in robes, central fully tiled bathroom and separate laundry.
Additional features include: security entrance, floor to ceiling windows, storage cage, secure undercover car park, access to building facilities including swimming pool, gymnasium and BBQ area.
Located within the Free Tram Zone, within walking distance to Southern Cross Station, and with easy Freeway access, you will also be spoilt for choice with local shopping and eateries, including Harbour Town, Spencer Outlet Centre, and Costco. The addition of cinemas and Woolworths to the area to be completed in 2019 will add to the sheer convenience of this ideal location.
